    Format[edit]

    • Group Stage:
      • Four double-elimination format (GSL) groups
        • Each group has 4 teams
        • All matches are Bo3
      • Top two teams from each group advance to the Playoffs
    • Playoffs:
      • Double-Elimination bracket
      • All matches (excl. Grand Final) are Bo3
      • Grand Final is Bo5
